{"tid":646233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"情困男摩士公園上吊 送院不治","createTime":"2018-04-29T00:20:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T00:40:33.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e265bc39e77c3d2ba5e78cabd580dc954d0a0f1a","tid":646233,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T00:20:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180429/large/1524953665_050b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180429%2Flarge%2F1524953665_050b.jpg&h=3c9fdb71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吊頸男子送院搶救。(黎志偉攝)<br />\n<br />\n黃大仙鳳舞街40號摩士公園，清晨5時15分，一名中年男子在涼亭用床單上吊，保安員發現報警。消防員到場解下，昏迷送院搶救，惜終告不治。警方現場撿獲空酒樽及相片等物品，初步懷疑涉及感情問題，調查沒有可疑。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180429/58131292\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180429%2F58131292&d=rkM8dvoGC4zeQMu%2F0UsLqQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=84e3ddd6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180429%2F58131292&h=d4b3149b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180429/58131292</a>"},{"pid":"ab555316827bd56497c8ea2d6fbd6e3a841ea729","tid":646233,"uid":141367,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T00:21:14.000Z","msg":"想問佢拎住果舊咩黎？"},{"pid":"404054179791c9a63606e033e85e63a659b79ec4","tid":646233,"uid":22218,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ab555316827bd56497c8ea2d6fbd6e3a841ea729","tid":646233,"uid":141367,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T00:21:14.000Z","msg":"想問佢